                <note rend="inline" type="source">704.5483/23: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the Minister in Egypt</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Howell</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1926-08-20T18:00:00-04:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 20, 1926—6 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>18. (1) Report briefly by telegraph action taken on Department’s written
                    instruction 276 of July 7.</p>
                <p>(2) Have you arranged with British Residency for formal transfer of Swiss
                    interests?</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Harrison</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
